<template>
	<view class="page">
		<lili-universal-filter
			title="新增采购记录"
			:showBack="true"
			:showSearch="false"
			:showHome="true"
			homePath="/pages/suppliers/index"
			backgroundColor="#EEF2F7"
		/>


		<scroll-view style="flex:1" class="page-scroll">

			<view class="page-content">
				<view class="hero-card">
					<text class="hero-title">采购记录录入页</text>
					<text class="hero-desc">当前已接入从供应商菜单进入的跳转，后续可以在这里补采购单表单。</text>
				</view>

				<view class="info-card">
					<text class="info-label">供应商ID</text>
					<text class="info-value">{{ supplierIdText }}</text>
				</view>

				<view class="hint-card">
					<text class="hint-text">请基于该供应商补充采购时间、采购金额、备注和附件等字段。</text>
